race.description: Sires On Ice Laurels F Division1
race.comment: TIMES FLYING (4) goes very well this trip starting 12 times for six wins and four minors. Scored by a neck last time (25.89) in a Free For All over 461m at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. FUEL ON FOUR (5) was last seen getting around 461m at this track in a fast 26.06 for a 1.3 lengths success. Smart winner latest and looks a key chance on that form. BELLARINE BEAUTY (2) struggled to get involved last start at Sandown, but prior to that won by a long neck at Warragul (26.29) beating Pretty Elle in a Mix 6/7 on September 26. Cannot be taken lightly. BLUE TROMBONE (1) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.
